title: EA Sports FC 24 - Official UEFA Euro 2024 Announcement Trailer
description:
EA Sports FC 24 is welcoming the most prestigious championship in Europe UEFA Euro 2024 to the game as a free in-game update. Players who play EA Sports FC 24 by January 16, 2024 will be able to gain access to one of Europe’s biggest stars as an exclusive, untradeable Ultimate Team Player item such as Jack Grealish or Federico Chiesa. UEFA Euro 2024 arrives to EA Sports FC 24 in Summer 2024 for PlayStation 4, PlayStation 5, Xbox One, Xbox Series S|X, and Nintendo Switch.

title: Sonic Superstars is Good, But It’s Not Classic Sonic
description: With Sonic Dream Team on its way, let’s take a look back at Sonic’s latest adventure in Sonic Superstars. Sonic Superstars is the latest Sonic game unleashed into the wild, with claims of being a thrilling new take on the Classic Sonic experience. After having spent an extensive amount of time with the game, Sonic Superstars is missing quite a few elements that truly encapsulates Classic Sonic in the Sonic the Hedgehog franchise. #SonicSuperstars is good, but the way it handles boss battles, special stages, and the chaos emeralds feels like a misrepresentation of Classic Sonic, especially when you compare it to how Sonic Mania—the BEST modern representation of Classic Sonic—handled those same gameplay elements. This is Akeem’s detailed opinion on Sonic Superstars, how it holds up to the other classic Sonic games, and maybe if it’s better than Sonic Mania.

title: Hogwarts Legacy: How to Change Your Gear Appearance (Transmog)
description:
Hogwarts Legacy is now available on Nintendo Switch, however, this video was made using the Xbox Series X, PlayStation 5, and PC versions of the game.

Hogwarts Legacy is chock full of gear, whether it be neckwear, cloaks and robes, outfits, and even facewear. But if you’re looking to keep appearances, mixing and matching gear to ensure you’re receiving the best stats possible won’t always provide the best appearance. Thankfully, Hogwarts Legacy utilizes a transmog system, which allows you to essentially activate cosmetic overrides for all types of gear. So, if your wizard fancies themself a fashionista, this video will explain everything you need to know about using the transmog system to change your gear appearance in Hogwarts Legacy.

#IGN #Gaming #HogwartsLegacy

title: A soliloquy, from our favorite Cheez. Presented by @CHEEZIT
How To Fix the Metal Gear Solid: Master Collection on PC (With Mods)
description:
Want to know how to fix the Metal Gear Solid Master Collection with mods? We've got you covered with our selection of the best MGS Master Collection mods for PC!

It's safe to say that the Metal Gear Solid: Master Collection Volume 1 was disappointing, lacking further enhancements compared to the Metal Gear Solid HD Collection released by Bluepoint Games in 2011. This brand new compilation of remastered ports is missing custom resolutions, ultra-widescreen support, FOV fixes, features lower quality audio, and much more.

So, how do we go about fixing that? Well, with mods, of course! MGS PC mods such as the MGSM2Fix, MGSHDFix, and other projects, allow us to breathe some new life into the MGS trilogy, while also introducing new features such as the MGS 3 Snake Eater crouch walking, something that was exclusive to the Nintendo 3DS Remake!
